### Get all milestones
GET {{BASE_URL}}/milestones

### Get a single milestone by ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/milestones/1

### Create a new milestone
POST {{BASE_URL}}/milestones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Milestone",
  "dealId": 1,
  "status": "pending"
}

### Update a milestone by ID
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/milestones/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Delete a milestone by ID
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/milestones/1
